
           =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=- Half Elf  -=-=-=-=-=-=

    Half-elves are a mixture of Elves and Humans.  Generally,
they are smarter and faster than humans though not as strong.


SUMMARY:

Dex: Above Avg       Str: Avg        Con: Above Avg 
Int: Avg       Wis: Above Avg       Char: Above Avg

Sight: Above Avg
HP Regen: Nil
SP Regen: Above Avg
Natural Weaponry: Standard (Above Avg)
Natural Armour: Nil
Ambidextry: Nil
Innate spells/skills: One skill
Exp Modifier: Nil

